releaseData.title: Leliel / Gaghiel (Versions)
releaseData.description: The initial plan for College Hill's abandoned Neon Genesis Evangelion-themed album also included remixes for each of the 17 tracks to be released alongside the original pieces. Now in 2020, the remixes to 'Leliel' and 'Gaghiel' are being released in remastered form alongside their originals.
